entries.title: Get This FREE VR FPS On Quest 2 While You Can!
entries.description:
Breachers just released in Alpha on Quest 2! Breachers is a 5v5 tactical FPS similar to Rainbow Six Siege but in VR! Get it for free and play it during the Alpha / Beta while you can! 

Join the Breachers Discord to get access to the Alpha on Quest 2 for FREE here;
http://breachersvr.com/discord

Wishlist Breachers on Steam here;
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1922010

Let me know what you think of Breachers on Quest 2 in the comments below...

Thanks for watching []-)
